The UK’s finest fright film festival is up and running and I’m at the frontline for The People’s Movies to bring genre fans news of the very latest in cutting-edge horror entertainment.

Get ready to fill up that must watch list as we embark on DAY ONE.

The bloodied stairway of horror awaits

Jacobi

There is some good news for fans of the Master. In this article, there is news of Derek Jacobi returning to reprise the role of the War Master. What is going to happen, you may ask. Well, last year he came back to Doctor Who when he reprised his role as the Master in Doctor Who: The War Master – Volume One with Big Finish production.
